'''Sinte''' (Sinti) si [[Romane manusha]] so avilen (15to [[shelbersh]]este) kay akanutne [[them]]a [[Jermaniya]] tay [[Estrexa]]. Palal kodya rigyarden pen pe duy droma: le ''Eftavagarya'' tay le ''Estraxarya''. Le Eftavagarya gelen ki akanutni [[Franchiya]] kay xamomen le thanutne romensa, navyarde [[Manusha]]. Le Estraxarya gelen kay [[Italiya]] tay [[Estutni Europa]] buteder kay thema [[Kroatiya]], [[Ungariya]], [[Transilvaniya]], [[Chexiya]] thai [[Slovakiya]].

Mashkar lenge si bare [[bashavno|bashavne]] vay [[gilavno|gilavne]], sar sas o [[Django Reinhardt]], vi ando khelsastimasko (sportesko) umal, sar o [[Johann  Trollmann]].

== Sinte Romani ==
Sinte han [[Romane Menshî]] yon Wella an o 15to shelbershesto klan ko [[Them]]a [[Gadchkeno]] un [[Walchi]]. I Sinte  koya  penen les ap duy droma: 
I ''Eftavagariya'' un i ''Estrachariya''. I Eftavagariya
Nashas klan ko them [[Valshi]] koya kharella yon [[Manush]]. I Estrachariya Nashas klan i thema [[Italiya]] un ani [[Osteskro Evropa]] butedar thema [[Kroatiya]], 
[[Ungariya]],  [[Transilvaniya]],  [[Shechiya]] un [[Slovakiya]].

Sinte hin bare [[Bashepangre]], Yek vas O [[Django Reinhardt]]. Un an i Kelsastepen (Sporto) O [[Johann Trollmann|Yohan Rukeli Trollmann]] O baro ''Boksa''.

